---
title: "Viewed Product"
---
The **Viewed Product** trigger activates a flow when a contact views a specific product on your website or app.

- **Note:** This Trigger is a part of [BigCommerce](https://support.salesmate.io/hc/en-us/articles/6774740880153-Introduction-and-Installation-of-BigCommerce) Integration

- **Topics covered:** -
- [How to Configure Viewed Product Trigger](#how-to-configure-viewed-product-trigger)

- [Practical Example](#practical-example)

### How to Configure Viewed Product Trigger

While creating the Trigger Based Flows select **Viewed Product** trigger

![mceclip0.png](./images/mceclip0-27.png)

Once the **Viewed Product** trigger is selected, you'll need to configure it by filling in the following details:

- **Name:** Assign a clear and descriptive name to identify the trigger.

- **Description:** Provide a brief explanation of what the trigger does.

- **Select Store:** Choose the BigCommerce store where the cart activity occurs.

- **Contact:** Specify any contact properties that need to match before a contact enters this flow.

- **BigCommerce:** Set conditions based on product-related properties that must be met before the trigger is activated.Once the configuration is completed, hit **Save**.

![mceclip1.png](./images/mceclip1-32.png)
